<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remind-of">remind … of …</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>使……想起……</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bill reminded him of the day years ago when they had first met.
比尔使他想起多年前他们初识的那一天。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Brad was Jane’s brother!
——布拉德是简的兄弟！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— No wonder he reminded me so much of Jane!
——难怪他让我觉得他那么像简呢。</p></div></div>